  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Village Montana Hotel is offered on a bed and breakfast board basis, or you can upgrade to 'Half Board'. This will include breakfast and evening meals (drinks are not included). Please note that on selected dates this hotel is only offered on half board.</p>
<p>Breakfast is a continental buffet breakfast with some additional hot options, usually served from 07:30 – 10am. This is taken in the Restaurant ‘Les Chanterelles’ which is located in the hotel.</p>
<p>Enjoy a five course à la carte evening meal with choice of menu and waiter service at 'Les Chanterelles', a traditional French restaurant. Or book into their other two restaurants - choose between 'La Chaumiere' (Savoyarde specialities) or a traditional brasserie 'La Place' in Chalet Montana Platon at the entrance to the complex.</p>
<p>The restaurants can also be booked and paid for locally if you stick to the bed and breakfast board basis. Opening times may vary, but are usually from 7 – 9:30pm. Please note that some dishes may have an additional supplement.</p>
<p>Christmas Dinner and New Years Galas are included.</p>
<p>Earlier meal times for children are available (on request, during French school holidays).</p>
<p><strong>Compulsory half board dates</strong></p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>23rd December</li>
<li>20th December</li>
<li>10th February</li>
<li>17th February</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
