  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Village Montana is in a great location, benefitting from having a central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes Le Lac</a> and offering ski in/ ski out access to the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a></p>
<h2>Skiing on your doorstep</h2>
<p>You'll enjoy being close to the slopes, which makes it easy to access the incredible <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a>. The hotel's location is excellent, near to the centre of Tignes Le Lac. It is elevated and sunny, making it a delightful and unique place to stay.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes- Val d'Isere Ski Area</a>, there is nowhere nicer to be than in the hotels wellness area. Featuring a heated outdoor pool, and a spa area with a sauna, hammam and hot tubs to sooth your achy ski legs. </p>
<p>The main building of the Village Montana has a cosy alpine feel with the combination of attractive stone and wood used throughout, creating a  warm and welcoming ambiance. The hotel also has a lovely bar lounge area with two pool tables, it is the perfect spot to enjoy a cocktail or mulled wine before dinner. There is also a games room to keep the children entertained.</p>
<h2>Savoyard specialities</h2>
<p>Treat your taste buds in the Chanterelles restaurant with its high-end French cuisine and generous selection of delightful cheese and desserts. Guests can also book dinner in the other restaurants which are apart of the Village Montana collection, including the La Chaumiere and Le Gourmet (supplements apply). </p>]]></description>
