  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin/ Double Comfort Rooms</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 30m². The rooms have a twin or double bedroom with additional bunk beds in an alcove off the main entrance hallway. This room type is also available for sole occupancy, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Privilege Rooms </strong>sleep two to five people and are around 33m². This room has a double bedroom (made up as a twin beds on request) and bunk beds. This room can also accommodate an additional third single bed. </p>
<p>Please note that safety regulations in France state that the upper bunk bed is not suitable for children under 6 years old.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have a double or twin beds</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Towels and linen</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Tea/coffee making facilities (available from reception)</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
